The paper proposes a method for efficient transfer learning and online adaptation in continuous control tasks using variational inference and latent variable models. This involves learning an explicit latent representation of unknown environment properties to facilitate generalization on novel environments at test time. The approach also uses a neural network ensemble that models dynamics and captures uncertainty over dynamics. Given these factors, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
